titleInfo.title: USA v. Ramos
titleInfo.subTitle: JUDGMENT as to Patrisia D. Ramos, Defendant pleaded guilty to Count I of the Information on 1/5/2007 and is sentenced to 3 years Probation with standard conditions and special conditions of supervision including 150 hours of Community Service; $25.00 special assessment and $2500.00 restitution. The $2500.00 restitution has been paid in full to Great Western Bank, Bellevue, NE. On the motion of the government, the Indictment is dismissed as to this defendant. Criminal Case Terminated as to defendant(s) Patrisia D. Ramos Ordered by Magistrate Judge Thomas D. Thalken.(PCV, ) (4 cc to US Marshal)
